query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('ati',
'connectedness',
'directory',
'fonts',
'games',
'gparted',
'hardware',
'homological-algebra',
'irreducible-polynomials',
'kde',
'limits-without-lhopital',
'riemann-zeta',
'ubuntu-one',
'uniform-convergence',
'vector-analysis')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name ilike '%cus%'
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
